subSubSection.paragraph:
General color as in male. FWs not covering last four abdominal tergites, slightly translucent, medium to light brown (
Fig. 2J
). Supra anal plate similar to the male, lighter (
Fig. 2K
). Subgenital plate wider than long, medium brown; posterior margin concave forming two lateral lobes light brown (
Fig. 2L
). Ovipositor shorter than TIII; dark brown almost black; ovipositor apex slightly serrulated laterally; medium to dark brown (
Fig. 2K, L
).
